# 12th Board Hub

**Your Ultimate CBSE Class 12 Study Resource Platform**

![CBSE Logo](https://www.cbse.gov.in/images//logo.png)

## 📚 Overview

12th Board Hub is a comprehensive digital study platform designed specifically for CBSE Class 12 students. It provides high-quality, handwritten notes from toppers across all three streams to help you excel in your board examinations.

## 🎯 Features

- **Toppers' Handwritten Notes**: Access high-quality notes written by CBSE toppers across all subjects
- **Stream-Specific Content**: Tailored resources for Arts/Humanities, Commerce, and Science streams
- **Multiple Study Resources**:
  - Board Syllabus
  - Previous Year Questions (PYQs)
  - Important Questions
  - Reference Videos
- **User-Friendly Interface**: Easy navigation and accessible design for seamless learning
- **Board Integration**: Direct links to official CBSE resources

## 🏫 Streams Offered

The platform serves three main Class 12th streams:

### 1. **Arts/Humanities**
   - Perfect for students interested in humanities and social sciences
   - Notes covering literature, history, geography, and more

### 2. **Commerce**
   - Tailored for commerce stream students
   - Comprehensive notes on accounting, economics, business studies, etc.

### 3. **Science**
   - Designed for science stream aspirants
   - In-depth notes on Physics, Chemistry, Biology, and Mathematics

## 📖 Study Materials Included

- **Board Syllabus**: Complete official CBSE syllabus for reference
- **Previous Year Questions (PYQs)**: Practice with actual board exam questions
- **Important Questions**: Curated questions likely to appear in exams
- **Video References**: Supplementary video resources for better understanding

## 🔗 Official Links

- **CBSE Official Website**: [www.cbse.gov.in](https://www.cbse.gov.in/)
- Directly access the official board syllabus and guidelines

